ated":3,"category":11,"tags":53,"description":54,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200511\u002F1897499725\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (14) - Graphics(2)","2020-05-11 07:30:15",[13,14,11,5,15],"前一篇介紹了基本的幾何圖形的繪畫，但是只介紹矩形，其實 PIXI 還有其他幾何圖形的繪畫，所以接下來就來講其他的幾何圖形囉",{"url":56,"title":57,"date":58,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":59,"description":60,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200504\u002F1045961354\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (13) - Graphics(1)","2020-05-04 08:10:50",[13,14,11,5,15],"接下來將會來介紹一點使用 PIXI 繪畫幾何圖形，最後會再來試著整合前面的技巧。",{"url":62,"title":63,"date":64,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":65,"description":66,"readingMinutes":36},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200427\u002F658713547\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (12) - mousemoveEvent(2)","2020-04-27 08:59:26",[13,14,11,5,15],"接下來講講關於 PIXI 其他的滑鼠操作吧~",{"url":68,"title":69,"date":70,"updated":3,"category":11,"tags":71,"description":72,"readingMinutes":17},"\u002Fjavascript\u002F20200420\u002F208566280\u002F","PixiJS V5 教學 (11) - mousemove","2020-04-20 08:35:59",[13,14,11,5,15],"前一篇介紹了使用鍵盤來移動圖片，那麼接下來就要來介紹使用滑鼠移動。",40,4,{"postCount":76,"tagCount":77},1035,1009,1784020401737]